data.description: DISCOVER THE EPITOME OF COZY COMFORT IN THIS SPACIOUS TWO-BEDROOM, ONE AND A HALF BATH BRICK RANCH NESTLED IN THE SOUGHT-AFTER COMMUNITY OF ST. CLAIR SHORES. BOASTING A CONVENIENT ONE CAR ATTACHED GARAGE, THIS HOME OFFERS BOTH FUNCTIONALITY AND CHARM. STEP INTO THE LARGE FENCED IN BACK YARD, COMPLETE WITH AN ADDITIONAL DETACHED GARAGE, PERFECT FOR STORING OUTDOOR FURNITURE OR PURSUING HOBBIES. INSIDE, THE ALLURE CONTINUES WITH HARDWOOD FLOORS THROUGHOUT, A CHARMING NATURAL FIREPLACE AND A PRACTICAL GALLEY KITCHEN. PLUS, WITH A BASEMENT ADDING EXTRA SPACE FOR STORAGE OR RECREATION, THIS HOME TRULY HAS IT ALL. AND LET'S NOT FORGET THE UNBEATABLE LOCATION- JUST A SHORT STROLL AWAY FROM THE VIBRANT SOCIAL DISTRICT OF ST. CLAIR SHORES, OFFERING A PLETHORA OF SHOPS, RESTAURANTS AND ENTERTAINMENT OPTIONS. SCHEDULE A SHOWING TODAY TO SEE EVERYTHING THIS PLACE HAS TO OFFER, THIS ONE WON'T LAST LONG!!
